title: People Holding Hands Light Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Two people holding hands, representing connection, partnership, ropersonce, or friendship between individuals with light and medium-dark skin tones.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji portrays two hands clasped together, showcasing a harmonious blend of light and medium-dark skin tones rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading. The soft, rounded edges and subtle gradients highlight the warmth and connection between individuals, conveying unity and partnership. This symbol of solidarity and mutual support is frequently used on Apple devices to represent relationships, agreement, or shared effort.
